In the [[Trandoshan/Legends|Trandoshan]] tradition of the [[Life debt/Legends|life debt]], the being to whom the debt was sworn was referred to as the Trandoshan's '''ghrakhowsk'''.

[[Marn Hierogryph]] became [[Slyssk]]'s ghrakhowsk after pretending to save Slssyk's life by pushing him out of the way of a falling piece of machinery.

